      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Thou shalt take no gift ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— From those whose causes are depending before thee; because, if thou dost not sell justice for it, thou wilt both seem and be tempted to do so. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The gift blindeth the wise ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— Bribes and interest cast a mist before the eyes, and bias the judgment and affections even of those who are otherwise wise and discerning. Besides, a habit of taking bribes will, in time, quite extinguish the light of reason, and destroy the sense of right and wrong. See ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ecclesiastes 7:7",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And perverteth the words of the righteous — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The words or sentence of those who would otherwise be righteous: or ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "perverteth the cause ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "of the righteous, and all he can say in his own defence, and and procures a wrong sentence to be given against him.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
