        "class": "bld",
        "text": "the matters or causes of the righteous, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " which may be understood not of the judges, but of the parties pleading, whose righteous cause is by this means perverted by the judge, and a wrong sentence given. ",
